---
import '../styles/about-hero.css';
---

<section class="about-hero">
  <div class="about-hero__bg"></div>
  <div class="container about-hero__container">
    <h1 class="about-hero__title">Beyond The Bottle: An Olfactory Chronicle</h1>
    <p class="about-hero__intro">
      We are the storytellers of scent. A dedicated collective exploring the history, artistry, and future of fragrance.
    </p>

    <h2 class="about-hero__subheading">Who We Are</h2>
    <p>Welcome to Mimya. We are not a store; we are a sanctuary for scent enthusiasts.</p>
    <p>
      In a world dominated by "sells to cart" buttons and fleeting trends, Mimya stands apart. We are an information and review collective dedicated to
      the deep exploration of perfumery. From the ancient incense trails of Mesopotamia to the synthetic molecules revolutionizing modern perfumery, we
      believe that every drop of perfume tells a story worth knowing.
    </p>
    <p>
      Our mission is simple: to demystify the complex world of fragrance. Whether you are a seasoned "fraghead" hunting for your next niche obsession
      or a newcomer trying to understand the difference between Eau de Toilette and Parfum, Mimya is your guide.
    </p>
    <p>We are obsessed with scent. And we want to share that obsession with you.</p>
  </div>
</section>
